          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Ending Forced Arbitration of Sexual Harassment Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a predispute arbitration agreement from being valid or enforceable if it requires arbitration of a sex discrimination dispute.</p> <p>The prohibition does not apply to an arbitration provision in a contract between an employer and a labor organization or between labor organizations, subject to limitations.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-12-26T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
